{"tid":2306590,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［戲院全線關閉？］其實咩叫做「公眾娛樂場所」","createTime":"2020-11-30T14:01:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T01:30:43.000Z","uid":48124,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"77799df7af304c63cca1edce945ee20532b19392","tid":2306590,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:01:58.000Z","msg":"本港第4波新冠肺炎疫情持續惡化，兩大主題樂園海洋公園及香港迪士尼樂園重開2個多月再次閉園！行政長官林鄭月娥今日（30日）公布多項防疫措施，包括遊戲機中心、遊樂場所、<span class=\"x-large\">公眾娛樂場所</span>，卡拉OK、麻雀天九耍樂場所和泳池，需於12月2日起停止營業14天。由於兩大主題樂園屬公眾娛樂場所，故此亦要關閉14天。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公眾娛樂場所即係戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68d8651936dbd2e5cee725d94adcdefef235492","tid":2306590,"uid":20624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"戲院好似係拎公眾娛樂場所牌照"},{"pid":"746166be15138f7f40150d97ef07e39046e9ff2a","tid":2306590,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"星期三後都冇得買飛啦"},{"pid":"d1ffebed02347b365b092604b733c44c67d276eb","tid":2306590,"uid":103693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"746166be15138f7f40150d97ef07e39046e9ff2a","tid":2306590,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:11:52.000Z","msg":"星期三後都冇得買飛啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T14:14:27.000Z","msg":"戲院正常安排都係最多買到後日既飛<br />\n如果星期四仲有開都要聽日先有得買<br />\n<br />\nbtw 上次戲院閂好似有另外列出?"},{"pid":"5d43dad1cd6760f80c52071be6dbc7723ec2c150","tid":2306590,"uid":145273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1ffebed02347b365b092604b733c44c67d276eb","tid":2306590,"uid":103693,"like":0,"dislike":0,